The '''1906 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their sixteenth ever season of organized football. The Keydets went an even 4-4 under 2nd-year head coach [[I. B. Johnson]].<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
